_sText:
This is a Fight(Fun?) Yard map I've decided to release. I'm quite pleased with the results, and I hope you will be too.

The map takes place in an abandonded, underground train tunnel depot, with 2 sets of tracks and a platform with a bombzone in the middle.

The map includes:
-Ventilation Shafts
-Bombzone in the center of the map
-38 Spawn Points in total
-Teams starting in opposite corners of the map

The map is great for both sniping, using shotguns, and regular weapons, since there are many different places with different ranges.

Please, if you try this map, post a review, telling me what you liked or how I can improve.


 / CrucixTM


Note: Do NOT decompile, edit or claim to be the owner of this map. This map was made by me, CrucixTM, and no one else. You are NOT allowed to post newer versions or copies of this map, or copy the name of it.
